## Vertrekken [/rise-api-core/haltes/vertrekken/{halte_id}/{num_results}]

### GET
+ Parameters
    + num_results (optional, number, `5`) ... Maximum aantal resultaten
    + halte_id (required, number, `200144`) ... Halte ID

+ Response 200 (application/json)

